<div class="comments-body nicolas"> 
<p>I have been using SVN happily for a long time. It&#39;s what CVS should have always been (revision number per file? WTF).</p>

<p>I still don&#39;t see the point of distributed SCMs. I guess I will keep staying away from them until I see the need. For now, they feel like a solution for a problem I don&#39;t have (just like almost all C++ features *used* to be, to me).<br />
</p>
<span class="comments-post" style="margin-left:20px">Nicolas on April  6, 2008  1:26 PM</span> 
